el_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/21920881"}}, "attached_info": "CjwIobT+7YzUu9cREAMaBjk0OTIxNSCfssSTBTAAONYMQANyCDIxOTIwODgxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1716912623.918721", "card_id": "Q_657060008", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一个成功的男领导会喜欢一个绝对忠诚，做事认真，业务能力强但是老实木讷长得不怎么样的女下属吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "领导很有能力，跟随他多年，鞍前马后，实心实意的伺候，绝对忠诚，业务能力自认不错，但是领导好像不太认可。本人较木讷，形象也不好。多年来任劳任怨，加班加点，工作量一人顶四个，对于领导布置工作从不讨价还价、从不打折扣，想领导所想、急领导所急，必要时会毫不犹豫替领导背锅，分忧解难，虽然关键时刻效果不一定咋样，但是尽心尽力了。不过这么多年从未得到领导一句正面肯定，也从未得到实质性利益，就纳闷自己在领导心目中到底是个什么位置。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-461d4a8ee64735760930696d5ab8df75_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657060008"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IobT+7YzUu9cREAMaCTEwODI5MTE4OSDUosKyBjAAOGdABHIJNjU3MDYwMDA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1716912623.919155", "card_id": "Q_656907404", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《鸣潮》角色面部五官排布正常吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b3c09917aa28f765957c4a04a207deb_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"